<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Timecard Rejected</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f8f8f8;">

  <div
    style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
    <!-- Logo -->
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <img src="https://nurses-now-facility.solz.me/fav.png" alt="Nurses Now" style="max-width: 200px;">
    </div>

    <h2 style="color: #d9534f;">Timecard Rejected</h2>
    <p>A timecard has been rejected for the following shift:</p>
    <p>
      <strong>Date and Time:</strong>
      <%= new Date(shiftData.start_date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long' , day: 'numeric' , year: 'numeric'
        }) %>
        at
        <%= new Date(shiftData.start_date + 'T' + shiftData.start_time).toLocaleTimeString('en-US', { hour: 'numeric' ,
          minute: 'numeric' , hour12: true }) %>
          to
          <%= new Date(shiftData.start_date + 'T' + shiftData.end_time).toLocaleTimeString('en-US', { hour: 'numeric' ,
            minute: 'numeric' , hour12: true }) %>
            <br>
            <strong>Location:</strong>
            <%= shiftData.facility.name %><br>
              <strong>Rejected By:</strong>
              Facility<br>
              <strong>Reason for Rejection:</strong>
              <%= shiftData.time_card.timecard_reject_reason.reason %>
    </p>

    <p>Please review the timecard and notify the concerned parties for further action.</p>

    <p>Thanks,<br>Nurses Now</p>
  </div>

</body>

</html>